notes: Price estimation; often called in swap TXs

label: Uniswap V4 Position Manager
notes: V4 LP handler; emits position events

label: Uniswap Permit2
notes: Signature-based approvals; common in modern Uniswap TXs

label: Uniswap V2 USDC/WETH Pair
notes: Example V2 pair address; many pairs exist
